last_episode_to_air.name: Broccoli’s Movie Night
last_episode_to_air.overview: It’s movie night, and Broccoli is showing her movie called Supertato: The Movie. But Evil Pea keeps changing the story to make herself look like the hero instead of Supertato.

name: Supertato
overview: Follow the adventures of Supertato, the world’s first potato superhero, as he tackles the mischievous Evil Pea in the supermarket aisles.

episodes.name: Tato Tower Takeover
episodes.overview: Evil Pea takes over the Tato Tower HQ and uses Carrot’s new security system to keep Supertato out. Supertato and Carrot work on a cunning ice cream plan to sneak back in.

episodes.name: Evil Pea's Big Freeze
episodes.overview: Evil Pea freezes the Veggies so she can take over the whole supermarket. Chilli’s heat unfreezes Supertato, who then races on lolly-stick skis to thwart Evil Pea and save the day.

episodes.name: Cheese Moon
episodes.overview: It’s a space race as Supertato helps Carrot fly her baguette rocket to become the first Veggie on the cheese moon, but halfway there Evil Pea makes them crash land.

episodes.name: Treasure in the Plant Aisle
episodes.overview: In the perilous plant aisle, Supertato and Evil Pea team up to find treasure as they have half a map each, but she tricks him and steals the map to find the treasure for herself.

episodes.name: Operation Jewel
episodes.overview: Evil Pea steals Tomato’s precious jewel. Supertato ventures to get it back by secretly lifting the jewel from Evil Pea’s crown and defeating a crowd of rampaging Mini Peas.

episodes.name: The Baddie Belt
episodes.overview: Evil Pea swaps Supertato's Tato-Belt with her evil Baddie-Belt, which has absurd and baffling functions. Supertato has to work out how to rescue Carrot and Pea with the Baddie-Belt.

episodes.name: Chilli to the Rescue
episodes.overview: Chilli decides to become a superhero called Super Chilli! His superhero skills are put to the test when Evil Pea covers Supertato in sticky honey, but Chilli’s heat saves the day.

episodes.name: Turnip of Terror
episodes.overview: Evil Pea tricks Supertato and the Veggies, who fall into the deli counter and come face to face with the Turnip of Terror. They escape with help from the not-so-scary Turnip.

episodes.name: Veggies Gotta Dance
episodes.overview: Supertato’s dancing is too powerful and destructive, but when he has to face Evil Pea in a dance-off to save his trapped friends, he soon realises his moves can save the day.

episodes.name: Banana's Star Appeal
episodes.overview: Banana Superstar’s show is stopped when Evil Pea steals his peel. Supertato races against him to get it back, but trouble hits when a giant banana statue collapses onto the stage.

episodes.name: Spooky Day
episodes.overview: Supertato runs in fright when Pumpkin tries to make friends with him, but he later realises she needs his help as she’s stuck in the air hanging from balloons set up by Evil Pea.

episodes.name: Pea's Power Suit
episodes.overview: Evil Pea wears a giant powersuit so powerful it knocks Supertato across the supermarket aisles. Carrot and Supertato plan to outsmart Evil Pea so she’ll lose her new powers.

episodes.name: Double Doughnut Rescue
episodes.overview: Evil Pea plunges Broccoli and Carrot into the doughnut toppings simultaneously, and Supertato almost quits being a superhero when he can’t save his two friends at the same time.

episodes.name: Evil Pea Takes a Break
episodes.overview: The Cobs try to capture Supertato while Evil Pea is on holiday, but it goes wrong resulting in Evil Pea getting covered in flour and custard over in the bath products aisle.

episodes.name: Super Birthday
episodes.overview: Supertato is delighted when Evil Pea comes to his birthday party, but Carrot is suspicious. Soon Evil Pea unleashes the Mini Peas, who try to steal Supertato’s birthday present.

episodes.name: Winter Wonderland
episodes.overview: Evil Pea thinks the Veggies won’t like it when she covers the supermarket in ice, but instead they have the best snow day ever, so she creates a giant snowball to ruin their fun.

episodes.name: The Good, the Bad and the Prickly
Wishing Tree
episodes.overview: Evil Pea blows all the lanterns away during the Lantern Festival. Supertato struggles to get them all back and needs Broccoli’s help to save the day.

episodes.name: Grape Kids' Super Camp
episodes.overview: Supertato leads the Grape Kids at Super Camp, but Evil Pea takes over with her Ice Camp.

episodes.name: Operation Kiwi
episodes.overview: Supertato, Carrot and Tomato are exploring in the plant aisle when they hear a strange noise. They follow the noise and meet the famous Kiwi the Explorer, who needs their help.

episodes.name: Museum Mischief
episodes.overview: Evil Pea pretends to help Supertato and Carrot train for crime prevention, but she tricks them and steals a mobile phone. Supertato and Carrot have a clever plan to get it back.

episodes.name: Broccoli Flies Again
episodes.overview: Evil Pea asks for flying lessons when Broccoli flies her paper plane into her freezer. Evil Pea doesn’t let Broccoli know that she intends to fly high to take over Tato Tower.

episodes.name: Tin Can Games
episodes.overview: It’s the Tin Can Games and Evil Pea wants to win the Tin Can Trophy. She cheats in the final race by putting a magnet on Supertato’s back to stop him from going super fast.

episodes.name: Tablet Takeover
episodes.overview: The Veggies are delighted with a new tablet they’ve found. When they’re not looking, Evil Pea turns the tablet to evil mode. Soon the tablet takes over the supermarket.

episodes.name: Carrot's Big Top
episodes.overview: Carrot is starring in her own circus and thinks that Supertato is trying to steal her limelight. She soon realises that Supertato is trying to rescue her from Evil Pea’s meddling.

episodes.name: Undercover Tomato
episodes.overview: Tomato paints himself green and goes undercover as a Mini Pea to discover how Evil Pea is firing them at Tato Tower. He makes an unexpected new Mini Pea friend.

episodes.name: Toy Aisle Trouble
episodes.overview: Evil Pea takes all the toys in the supermarket for herself and the Cobs to play with. Supertato climbs a big wall of boxes to try and get the toys back.

episodes.name: Peas and Quiet
episodes.overview: There are odd noises in the supermarket. Supertato discovers that Evil Pea and the Mini Peas are asleep and walking through the supermarket. Supertato tries to get them back to bed.

episodes.name: Cereal Mountain
episodes.overview: Chilli tries to reach the top of Cereal Mountain without the help of Supertato’s gadgets.

episodes.name: Dragon Boat Beats
episodes.overview: Supertato and Evil Pea race one another in the Dragon Boat Race Festival on Ice. Evil Pea’s team seem to be the fastest, until Supertato helps his team to row in harmony.

episodes.name: How to Be a Supertato
episodes.overview: In Tato Tower, Supertato shows the Grape Kids a film on how to be a Supertato like him.

episodes.name: The Throne Thief
episodes.overview: Someone has stolen Evil Pea’s throne, and all clues point to Supertato as the thief!

episodes.name: Broccoli Alone
episodes.overview: Supertato is out chasing a milkshake robot and leaves Broccoli in charge of Tato Tower. Evil Pea tries to take over the tower, but Broccoli puts on a great defence.

episodes.name: Pea Repeats
episodes.overview: Supertato is due to receive the Best Hero Award, but Evil Pea decides she should get it. Carrot tells her she needs to defeat herself to win the award.

episodes.name: Da Veggie Code
episodes.overview: Supertato’s Tato belt gets locked inside a glass case for an exhibition, but Tomato can’t remember the code to get it out again, and Supertato needs it back to defeat Evil Pea.

episodes.name: Double Trouble
episodes.overview: Supertato and Carrot are looking for ice and think Evil Pea has become kind by giving them some. They soon realize it’s not Evil Pea after all.

episodes.name: Carrot Powers Up
episodes.overview: Carrot wants to become superstrong, so she restores Evil Pea’s robot suit for herself.

episodes.name: Evil Pea’s Veggie Vision
episodes.overview: Evil Pea is tricked by lots of Supertatoes who appear all over the supermarket.

episodes.name: Come Back Cobs
episodes.overview: The Cobs have finally had enough of Evil Pea’s ungratefulness and team up with Supertato.

episodes.name: Big Net Rescue
episodes.overview: Carrot is determined to save Supertato from Evil Pea’s trap without help from Prickly Pear.

episodes.name: Moustache Mystery
episodes.overview: Broccoli is horrified when someone paints moustaches on photographs of her friends!

episodes.name: Waltzing Potato
episodes.overview: Evil Pea plans to freeze Supertato into an ice cube by pretending to teach him to dance.

episodes.name: Broccoli’s Movie Night
episodes.overview: It’s movie night, and Broccoli is showing her movie called Supertato: The Movie. But Evil Pea keeps changing the story to make herself look like the hero instead of Supertato.
